        </div>

        <hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #333;" />

        <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.5rem;">
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.6rem; font-size:0.9rem;">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2C8.134 2 5 5.134 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.866-3.134-7-7-7z" stroke="#eee" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5" stroke="#eee" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
            Carrera 3F Nº 32A - 13, Manizales - Colombia.
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.6rem; font-size:0.9rem;">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6.6 10.8c1.4 2.8 3.8 5.1 6.6 6.6l2.2-2.2c.3-.3.7-.4 1-.2 1.1.4 2.3.6 3.6.6.6 0 1 .4 1 1V20c0 .6-.4 1-1 1C10.6 21 3 13.4 3 4c0-.6.4-1 1-1h3.5c.6 0 1 .4 1 1 0 1.3.2 2.5.6 3.6.1.3 0 .7-.2 1L6.6 10.8z" stroke="#eee" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
            (+57) 313 831 1426
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.6rem; font-size:0.9rem;">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="#eee" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 010 20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 000 20" stroke="#eee" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
            <a href="https://www.technopharmed.com" target="_blank" style="color:#eee;">www.technopharmed.com</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #333;" />

        <div style="font-size:0.85rem; line-height:1.8; color:#ccc;">
          <p><strong style="color:#fff;">Directorio de Soporte</strong></p>
          <p>Gerencia: Ing. Juan Quintero &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="mailto:gerencia@technopharmed.com" style="color:#bbb;">gerencia@technopharmed.com</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Tel: 313 831 1426</p>
          <p>Administrativo: Claudia Santa &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="mailto:administrativo@technopharmed.com" style="color:#bbb;">administrativo@technopharmed.com</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Tel: 313 627 36 94</p>
          <p>Asistencia: Laura Uribe &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="mailto:asistente@technopharmed.com" style="color:#bbb;">asistente@technopharmed.com</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Tel: 318 837 6804</p>
        </div>

      </div>
